Ernest Sefton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Sefton 0 Ernest Sefton (born as Ernest Henry Tipton; 13 January 1883 in Hackney, London – 5 December 1954) was a British film actor. He was the brother of Violet Loraine. Ernest_Sefton ( born as Ernest_Henry_Tipton ; 13_January_1883 in Hackney , London – 5_December_1954 ) was a_British_film_actor .
